</div>

<!-- BINGO MODAL -->
<div id="bingo_modal" class="modal fade">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
    
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h3 class="modal-title">BINGO</h3>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Have the students choose a random selection of words on the screen 
          and write them on a sheet of paper in a grid. Have them use a...
          <ul>
            <li>5x5 grid if there are at least 25 words</li>
            <li>4x4 grid if there are at least 16 words</li>
            <li>3x3 grid if there are at least 9 words</li>
          </ul>
          Then click start. The words will appear in random order. Click next to
          proceed or back to verify. When a word is called, the student can cross
          it off. The first student to cross off all the words in a row wins.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- RECALL MODAL -->
<div id="recall_modal" class="modal fade">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
    
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h3 class="modal-title">RECALL</h3>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>All words will be displayed with images. Go over them until the class
          feels like they remember them fairly well. Then click START and a grid
          of cards will be shown face down below a search bar. Students call out 
          words and you type them into the search box. As you type, all words 
          that match will be highlighted. When there is only one, hit enter to 
          reveal the card. Continue untill all cards are revealed.</p>
        <p>You might also flip all cards that start with a certain letter. You
          can also flip a card by clicking on it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
